title: Walk it off: Stamps down Cats, clinch home field (CFL - Canadian Football League)
text: ( Source : CFL - Canadian Football League ) CFL.ca Staff HAMILTON -- Rene Paredes booted a 37-yard field goal with no time remaining to lift the Calgary Stampeders to a thrilling 23-20 win over the Hamilton Tiger-Cats on Friday Night Football .
